data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom single family home, built in 2020, offers modern comfort and thoughtful design. As you step inside, you'll appreciate the spacious living areas and the abundance of natural light.The well-appointed kitchen is equipped with a refrigerator, stove, microwave, and dishwasher - perfect for your culinary adventures. The convenience of a washer and dryer adds to the appeal.The master bedroom features his and her closets and dual bathroom sinks, providing ample storage and personal space. The master bathroom offers both a relaxing tub and a separate shower.Outside, you'll find a fenced-in backyard and a screened-in lanai, creating the ideal setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.
